Alignment Zones

Check if nodes are close to a zone, but not in or touching it.

This is a TTF, but this test is only for CFF fonts.

Cabin Regular (Cabin-Regular.ttf)

OS/2

useTypoMetrics

If the hhea metrics match the sTypo metrics and not usWin metrics the fsSelection useTypoMetrics flag should be True.

OK: fsSelection useTypoMetrics flag is True.

Error

Cabin Regular (Cabin-Regular.ttf)

OS/2

WWS

If no NID 21 and 22, 'OS/2' fsSelection flag for WWS should be True.

'OS/2' fsSelection flag for WWS should be True but is False.

Pass

Cabin Regular (Cabin-Regular.ttf)

OS/2

Cabin Italic (Cabin-Italic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Cabin-Italic', Everything looks good.

Cabin Medium Regular (Cabin-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Cabin-Medium', Everything looks good.

Pass

, most common Monotype license test is:
This font software is the property of Monotype Imaging Inc., or one of its affiliated entities (collectively, Monotype) and its use by you is covered under the terms of a license agreement. You have obtained this font software either directly from Monotype or together with software distributed by one of the licensees of Monotype. This software is a valuable asset of Monotype. Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. You may not copy or distribute this software. If you have any questions concerning your rights you should review the license agreement you received with the software. You can learn more about Monotype by clicking here: www.monotype.com.

Cabin Medium Regular (Cabin-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Cabin' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium' = NID 1 'Cabin Medium'.

Pass

Cabin Medium Italic (Cabin-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Cabin' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium Italic' = NID 1 'Cabin Medium' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Cabin SemiBold Regular (Cabin-SemiBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Cabin-SemiBold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Cabin SemiBold Italic (Cabin-SemiBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Cabin-SemiBoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Cabin SemiBold Italic (Cabin-SemiBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Cabin' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold Italic' = NID 1 'Cabin SemiBold' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Pass

Cabin Bold (Cabin-Bold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'Cabin-Bold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. NID 6 is 'Cabin-BoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Cabin Condensed Italic (CabinCondensed-Italic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'CabinCondensed-Italic', Everything looks good.

Cabin Condensed Medium Regular (CabinCondensed-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'CabinCondensed-Medium', Everything looks good.

Cabin Condensed Medium Regular (CabinCondensed-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Cabin Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium' = NID 1 'Cabin Condensed Medium'.

Cabin Condensed Medium Italic (CabinCondensed-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'CabinCondensed-MediumItalic', Everything looks good.

Cabin Condensed Medium Italic (CabinCondensed-MediumItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Cabin Condensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium Italic' = NID 1 'Cabin Condensed Medium' + 'Space' + NID 2 'Italic'.

Cabin Condensed SemiBold Italic (CabinCondensed-SemiBoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'CabinCondensed-SemiBoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Cabin Condensed Bold (CabinCondensed-Bold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

NID 6 is 'CabinCondensed-Bold', Everything looks good.

Cabin Condensed Bold Italic (CabinCondensed-BoldItalic.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'CabinCondensed-BoldItalic', Everything looks good.

Info

Cabin Regular (Cabin-Regular.ttf)

kern
